{"tid":1302414,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"基本法阻礙真普選嘅證據","createTime":"2019-07-10T02:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T04:16:59.000Z","uid":173326,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"88443a673cb23310cbff305f9dbc0963aa3b2089","tid":1302414,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T02:45:24.000Z","msg":"好心自己睇下基本法，唔好咁懶齋睇新聞/fb啦。基本法：<a href=\"https://www.basiclaw.gov.hk/pda/tc/basiclawtext/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.basiclaw.gov.hk%2Fpda%2Ftc%2Fbasiclawtext%2Findex.html&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8CvGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=819d5471\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.basiclaw.gov.hk/pda/tc/basiclawtext/index.html</a><br />\n文件24、25、26係相輔相成，令到真正普選不可能實現。<br />\n如果照基本法去推所謂普選，香港就會成為大陸2.0，得假普選假民主。<br />\n831框架並非中央隨口up，係已經正式入左做基本法文件24。<br />\n你要反對831，就要反對基本法，唔好奢望中央會肯修改/撤回呢幾條文件，佢搞咁多野就係唔想你有真普選。<br />\n即使中央為平民怨肯收回呢啲條文，俾一屆真普選你，只要基本法繼續授予人大至高無上嘅權力，佢隨時都可以加入更多條文去限制你，因為基本法賦予佢地咁嘅權力。<br />\n咁可以點？唯一答案： 香港 _ _"},{"pid":"b9b81059e556f3836f39b6a322d22f85c630f5d1","tid":1302414,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T03:12:26.000Z","msg":"link都貼埋喇，仔細睇下相關條文，你先知道要點先可以保護香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c94b8f0e6cc0b28ec5019ee23331539fe8d6ad14","tid":1302414,"uid":166117,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T03:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BETaxif.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBETaxif.png&h=85abde06&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qaQzYYg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqaQzYYg.png&h=76ab0237&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf0facbe0d6365e92fcb46188b0ef0ca59e17f28","tid":1302414,"uid":173326,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T05:20:20.000Z","msg":"保皇黨用「符合基本法」呢句去利用法治名義，屢次包裝賣港行為，包括高鐵、dq、假普選等等。<br />\n我地亦應該睇清基本法嘅真面目，從條文內容搵